# API Reference

Complete documentation for all CFL UI components and CSS design tokens.

---

## Components

All components are used via Jekyll includes:

```liquid
{% include components/button.html text="Click me" variant="primary" %}
```

---

### Button

Versatile button component for actions and links.

```liquid
{% include components/button.html
   text="Button Text"
   variant="primary"
   size="md"
   href="/link"
%}
```

| Parameter | Type | Default | Description |
|-----------|------|---------|-------------|
| `text` | string | "Button" | Button label text |
| `label` | string | ‚Äî | Alias for `text` |
| `variant` | string | "primary" | Style variant: `primary`, `secondary`, `ghost`, `danger`, `success` |
| `size` | string | "md" | Size: `sm`, `md`, `lg` |
| `href` | string | ‚Äî | Link URL (renders as `<a>` if provided) |
| `url` | string | ‚Äî | Alias for `href` |
| `target` | string | ‚Äî | Link target: `_blank`, etc. |
| `rel` | string | ‚Äî | Link rel attribute |
| `icon` | string | ‚Äî | Icon/emoji before text |
| `icon_right` | string | ‚Äî | Icon/emoji after text |
| `block` | boolean | false | Full-width button |
| `type` | string | "button" | Button type (when no href) |

