## CSS Variables

All design tokens are defined as CSS custom properties in `:root`.

### Color Palette

| Variable | Default | Description |
|----------|---------|-------------|
| `--bg` | `#fef9f3` | Page background |
| `--bg-alt` | `#f8edd8` | Alternate background |
| `--surface` | `#fffcf8` | Card/surface background |
| `--text` | `#2a1f1a` | Primary text color |
| `--text-muted` | `#6b5c52` | Secondary text color |
| `--accent` | `#e63946` | Primary accent (coral-red) |
| `--accent-hover` | `#c62d3a` | Accent hover state |
| `--accent-secondary` | `#038592` | Secondary accent (teal) |
| `--border` | `#e8dcc8` | Default border color |
| `--border-dark` | `#d4c4a8` | Darker border |
| `--shadow` | `rgba(42,31,26,0.1)` | Box shadow color |

### Semantic Colors

| Variable | Default | Description |
