### Customizing Theme

Override CSS variables in your own stylesheet:

```css
:root {
    --accent: #8b5cf6;  /* Purple accent */
    --accent-hover: #7c3aed;
    --font-heading: 'Playfair Display', serif;
}
```

Or use the Settings widget (gear icon) to change fonts and colors dynamically.

